changeling-hiveless-intro = You are Hiveless
changeling-hiveless-doctrine = Your Hive's Doctrine: Hunt your prey. Your approach is not of concern. So long as you are fed at the end of the day, that is all the ultimately matters.
changeling-hiveless-allies = Notes from your Hive: The ones that are also hiveless may share your prey. But the ones within hives have enough to go around. Do not let them steal your hunt. Exceptions can be made if someone adopts you into their Hive, in which you must abide by their Doctrines.
changeling-role-greeting-hiveless = You are [color=orange]not apart of a Hive.[/color]

changeling-pale-choir-intro = You are apart of the Pale Choir Hive.
changeling-pale-choir-doctrine = Your Hive's Doctrine: Preservation through erasure. Do not allow your true identity to be revealed. You must maintain secrecy at all costs.
changeling-pale-choir-allies = Notes from your Hive: It does not matter who you ally with. So long as they do not attempt to reveal your presence, you may hunt with anyone.
changeling-role-greeting-pale-choir = You are [color=orange]apart of the Pale Choir Hive.[/color]

changeling-swarm-of-ichor-intro = You are apart of the Swarm of Ichor Hive.
changeling-swarm-of-ichor-doctrine = Your Hive's Doctrine: Consume, subvert, multiply. Our territory must grow. While being quiet is not prohibited, a louder approach would allow for optimal expansion.
changeling-swarm-of-ichor-allies = Notes from your Hive: Teamwork is encouraged. We cannot spread our influence on a one man army. The more of us that are willing to co-operate with you, the better.
changeling-role-greeting-swarm-of-ichor = You are [color=orange]apart of the Swarm of Ichor Hive.[/color]

changeling-solstice-shroud-intro = You are apart of the Soltice Shroud Hive.
changeling-solstice-shroud-doctrine = Your Hive's Doctrine: Control from within. Manipulate your opposition to the best of you ability. Replace others, become one with them, and keep your disguise.
changeling-solstice-shroud-allies = Notes from your Hive: Do not work with others in long term. It becomes harder to maintain disguise. You may work with others temporarily but do not make the alliance more prolonged than is required.
changeling-role-greeting-solstice-shroud = You are [color=orange]apart of the Solstice Shroud Hive.[/color]

changeling-red-garden-intro = You are apart of the Red Garden Hive.
changeling-red-garden-doctrine = Your Hive's Doctrine: Evolve or perish. We are the superior life forms. But we are just. Do not take your enemies by suprise. Let them learn how superior we are.
changeling-red-garden-allies = Notes from your Hive: Work with others from the Hive as you will. The lesser hives may work with us. But make sure they know they are of a lesser hive. Nobody is superior to us, and we will not work with anyone that doesn't accept that.
changeling-role-greeting-red-garden = You are [color=orange]apart of the Red Garden Hive.[/color]

changeling-crownless-knights-intro = You are apart of the Crownless Knights Hive.
changeling-crownless-knights-doctrine = Your Hive's Doctrine: Invoke fear. Spread fear, chaos, terror amongst the crew. It is amusing to watch your prey squirm.
changeling-crownless-knights-allies = Notes from your Hive: We work with none. Not even amongst our own hive. Show them true fear on your own.
changeling-role-greeting-crownless-knights = You are [color=orange]apart of the Crownless Knights Hive.[/color]

changeling-false-light-intro = You are apart of the False Light Hive.
changeling-false-light-doctrine = Your Hive's Doctrine: Decieve, divide, disarm. Collapse trust and ensue chaos. That is our primary goal here. Utilise the chaos amongst the crew to your advantage.
changeling-false-light-allies = Notes from your Hive: Working with others is key. It allows us to cause more chaos. Go out of your way to assist others of us, willing or not. The more chaos, the better.
changeling-role-greeting-false-light = You are [color=orange]apart of the False Light Hive.[/color]
